These are different things you can do for managing wikis.

* `Wiki Listing` shows all of the wikis that are currently available. You can display this list in the sidebar.
* `Create Wikis` has different methods for creating or adding new wikis to Bob.
* `Rename Wikis` lets you rename or move existing wikis.
* `Delete Wikis` lets you delete existing wikis. This is permanent and can not be undone.

</$reveal>

